snippet.title: Farming Simulator 25 - Official Farming in Asia Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
Prepare to do some farming in East Asia. Tour the new farming environment, Hutan Pantai, in this latest Farming Simulator 25 trailer. This new map features two types of rice, specialized equipment for planting and harvesting, and water buffalo roaming the corrals. Farming Simulator 25 will be available on PC, Mac, PS5, and Xbox Series X/S on November 12, 2024.

#FarmingSimulator #FarmingSimulator25 #Gaming
